<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٠٢٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1018">أَبُو بَكْرِ بْنُ أَصْرَمَ </a>: أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3875">عَبْدُ اللهِ </a>: أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6279">مَعْمَرٌ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6737">هَمَّامِ بْنِ مُنَبِّهٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«سَمَّى النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> الْحَرْبَ خَُدْعَةً.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>